Val.description:
Imagine that you are doing a project "Best Presents" together with your friend. You have found some illustrations and want to share the news. Leave a voice message to your friend. In 2.5 minutes be ready to:
- give a brief description of the photos, justifying the choice of the photos for the project;
- say in what way the pictures are different, justifying the choice of the photos for the project;
- mention the advantages and disadvantages (1-2) of the two kinds of presents;
- express your opinion on the subject of the project - whether you would like to give someone a handmade present and why.

You will speak for not more than 3 minutes (12-15 sentences).

You have to talk continuously.

